QuestData.Title: The Dranosh'ar Blockade
QuestData.Description: You should head north from here, $n. Speak with Gor the Enforcer at the Dranosh'ar Blockade. He's been placed in charge of securing shipping lanes for Orgrimmar, and Skull Rock sits right next to his precious dock. I'm certain he'll be interested in picking up where we left off.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Gor the Enforcer at the Dranosh'ar Blockade in Durotar.
QuestData.RewardText: You're the one who handled the Burning Blade to the south? I've got ears in all kinds of places, $g boy: my girl;, and word travels fast.
